<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mstḥq kl ạlmjd yạ yswʿ)2
 kl rkbẗ tsjd lyk .. wạllsạn yʿtrf byk
 mstḥq kl ạlmjd yạ yswʿ
 2- (lmạ nyjy nqf qdạmk yạ yswʿ)2
 kl ʿạly ynḥny .. kl mhdwm ytbny
 lmạ nyjy nqf qdạmk yạ yswʿ
 3- (kẖly ḥḍwrk ymlạ ʿynynạ yạ yswʿ) 2
 ntgẖyr wʿynynạ tsẖwf .. mjdk bwjh mksẖwf
 kẖly ḥḍwrk ymlạ ʿynynạ yạ yswʿ</lyrics>
<title>mstḥq kl ạlmjd yạ yswʿ</title>
</song>